item.description:
Let’s meet for dinner and drinks at the Derryfield followed by dancing. Mama Kicks is a great band to dance to. The band starts at 9:30 so if you can’t make dinner, join us later for dancing. Hope to see you there. There is a 5.00 cover at 9PM so you may want to get there a little earlier :-)

I can be reached at 603-670-5025- Natalie

group.name: Fun in So. NH and Merrimack Valley

item.name: Dancing, Dinner and Drinks with Mama Kicks .
